## `input.ts` — `peekDirection()`

```ts
peekDirection(): Direction | null {
  return this.deriveDirection();
}
```

Non-destructive read: does not consume `bombQueued`. The existing
`getCurrentInput()` is still the only method that clears `bombQueued`.

