## `main.ts` wiring

### Instance
```ts
const predictor = new LocalPlayerPredictor();
```

### Render loop
```ts
const now = performance.now();
const me  = state.players[myPlayerId];
predictor.advance(input.peekDirection(), me?.speedMultiplier ?? 1.0, state.grid, now);
render(ctx!, state, myPlayerId, playerSlotMap, predictor.x, predictor.y);
```

### `room:state` IN_GAME handler
```ts
// Active player branch
const me = state.gameState.players[myPlayerId]!;
predictor.init(me.pixelX, me.pixelY);

// Spectator branch
predictor.reset();
```

### `game:tick` handler
```ts
const me = gameState.state?.players[myPlayerId];
if (me?.alive) predictor.reconcile(me.pixelX, me.pixelY);
```

### Reset sites
`predictor.reset()` called in: `WAITING`/`STARTING` branch, spectator branch,
`game:over` handler, `disconnect` handler.

